      • replayFlow

        protected PlatformPacket replayFlow(PlatformPacket packet)
                             throws Exception
        Delegates replay of the packet to ReplayStrategy.replay(PlatformPacket). The replay strategy is looked up from the OSGi service registry.
        Overrides:
        replayFlow in class PlatformFlowManager
        Parameters:
        packet - PlatformPacket to be replayed.
        Returns:
        an optionally updated PlatformPacket.
        Throws:
        Exception - if replay fails.
        See Also:
        PlatformPacket.deserialize(byte[]), PlatformPacket.serialize()
